              <span id="reviewTextContainer1403166023" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer11592920841841820011"><br/>4.5 - a re-read - not as good the second time around. I sort of knew the &quot;wow&quot; factor so that took away from it. I think I might have already reviewed another version so apologies if there are two reviews on here. Well, I did read it twice so maybe that&apos;s OK. <br/><br/>I love both main characters. Knew what they wanted ... each other! Sam sure is sexy.<br/><br/><img src='https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/hostedimages/1443597410i/16383838._SY540_.jpg' class='gr-hostedUserImg'/><br/>Jaine is a great heroine. Has a temper, has a backbone, has a sense of humour.<br/><br/><blockquote>
  <b>“If you&apos;re looking for Mr. Perfect, you‟re going to spend your whole life b</b></blockquote></span>
  <span id="freeText11592920841841820011" style="display:none"><br>4.5 - a re-read - not as good the second time around. I sort of knew the "wow" factor so that took away from it. I think I might have already reviewed another version so apologies if there are two reviews on here. Well, I did read it twice so maybe that's OK. <br><br>I love both main characters. Knew what they wanted ... each other! Sam sure is sexy.<br><br><img src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/hostedimages/1443597410i/16383838._SY540_.jpg" class="gr-hostedUserImg"><br>Jaine is a great heroine. Has a temper, has a backbone, has a sense of humour.<br><br><blockquote>
  <b>“If you're looking for Mr. Perfect, you‟re going to spend your whole life being disappointed, because he doesn‟t exist. You have to get the best deal you can, but there will always be problems.” </b>
</blockquote><br><br>And that is where all the trouble started. With "the List"!<br><br><img src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/hostedimages/1443597410i/16383841.jpg" class="gr-hostedUserImg"><br><img src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/hostedimages/1443597410i/16383839._SY540_.jpg" class="gr-hostedUserImg"><br><img src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/hostedimages/1443597410i/16383840.jpg" class="gr-hostedUserImg"><br><blockquote>
